  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Adiboo & Paziral's Secret is a 3D action adventure game with 12 levels. Players will take control of Adiboo and help rescue the citizens of peaceful Tonies Island from the threat of mysterious island. The mysterious island has a leader named Paziral. To unveil his secret player must come across five levels: volcano, lagoon, forest, temple, and metal island. The game is divided into platform, racing, and arcade stages.",
